      "title": "A 10-hour water cut in two areas of Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board says that the water supply to several areas of Colombo will be suspended for 10 hours tomorrow (20) and from 11:00 pm tomorrow to 9:00 am the next day (21).",
        "The Water Supply Board states that water supply to Colombo 5 and 6 will be suspended and Colombo 4 will be supplied with low pressure during that time."
      ],
